{"tid":2017141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有議員質疑政府派口罩 薛永恒強調銅有助殺病毒及細菌","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T05:15:58.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd87d0edd556fac8c2be2ee9ebee45845a31f743","tid":2017141,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"有議員質疑政府派口罩 薛永恒強調銅有助殺病毒及細菌<br />\n2020-05-15 HKT 09:54<br />\n<br />\n在立法會財委會上，有議員就「銅芯抗疫口罩」提出質疑。創新及科技局局長薛永恒表示，目前仍未完成「銅芯口罩」的供應工序，完成工作後會有審計報告，清楚交代涉及研發開支的8億元如何使用。<br />\n<br />\n薛永恒又說，世界上無一個實驗所，聲稱做到可以殺死新型肺炎病毒，而銅的功用有文獻確認， 當局是強調銅可以協助殺死病毒及細菌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526283-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526283-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=2e8575ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526283-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ba289007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526283-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7ed230f75ba6e02d4ee57f0edca79025767f9365","tid":2017141,"uid":184050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"氧化銅係Genocide ，即係對你都有害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87783068dc91f665882a7e4c3385f77e9429e0a1","tid":2017141,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:33:34.000Z","msg":"幫手打tvb戰線 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［cctvb我屌你老母］去無良廣告商fb洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2017022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2017022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5066a6cd57e67785717a79bd1d2eed207aa6998","tid":2017141,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"